1 ip link set interface up/down to up or down an intf
2 ip addr add xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx/netmask brd + dev intf-name 
3 ip route add xxx/xxx dev name
4 ip route add xxx/xxx  via xxx.xxx dev name
5 ip route add default  via xxx.xxx dev name
(a route is xx.xx.xx.xx/netmask)

ip route del  xxx/xxx

ip link show
ip addr show
ip route show 
(use -s to show more thing)

